profile:
National Star Roofing is a family owned and operated company specializing in sloped and flat roofs in the Calgary area since July 2003. It has been rated the Best Roofing Company/Contractor in Calgary by HomeStars and holds an A+ rating with the BBB. 

National Star Roofing is a Preferred Contractor with Owen's Corning, is fully licensed and insured with WCB and is covered by a General Liability Insurance of up $10 million per job. 

Consistently quality work, attention to detail and great customer service is what tells us apart. 
Customer satisfaction is our first priority. 
No payment is required until the job is complete to the owner's satisfaction. Extra charges apply to payments by credit card. 

National Star Roofing's services include sloped roof replacements as well as flat roof repairs/replacements.
services:
Asphalt shingles.
SBS Membrane Flar roofing systems. 
Roofing contracting services.
Re-roof.
Roof Repair.
Residential roofing.
Commercial roofing.
Flat roofing.
name: National Star Roofing Inc.

profile:
No Limit Exteriors offers Full Medicine Hat Roofing, Exteriors and Restoration Solutions. Servicing both Commercial and Residential buildings in Medicine Hat Alberta and area.
We are a locally owned company who thrives on keeping Medicine Hat home owners and businesses satisfied with their homes and buildings, at affordable rates.
Free Estimates and Financing are Available.
Contact us today 403-952-2484
https://nolimitexteriors.com

We are a professional full exteriors company, that specializes in roofing. All of our roofers are highly skilled with 16+ years of experience. All of our supplied shingles are Canadian made with a variety of colors.

*** Complete Exteriors Service in Medicine Hat and Area ***
***                    Commercial and Residential                      ***

We provide: 
• Re-roofing - shingle roof and flat roof replacement
• Roof repair, including fixing Roof Leaks
• Eaves troughs and downspouts
• Soffits and Fascia
• Siding
• Skylights
• Insulation
• Flat roofs
* Gutter cleaning
* Pressure Washing
* Painting
* Fence and deck builds and repairs

** Emergency Repairs and Insurance Claims
** Hail damage Experts

***    Free Estimates     ***
*** Financing Available ***

100% Insured and licensed
10 year workmanship warranty

We take pride in our work and customer satisfaction is always guaranteed.
From Top to Bottom, your complete Exteriors Solution. Done Right the First time.

profile:
All Site Exteriors Inc is a Canadian business that provides talented and professional contractors for all kinds of exterior needs. We have more than 20 years of active industry experience in providing cost-effective and precise exterior improvement solutions in Medicine Hat.

Our wide range of services include:

   ** Shutters
   ** Replacement windows
   ** Roofing
   ** Walls having vinyl siding
   ** Fascia & soffit
   ** Patio & porch ceilings

We are available on weekdays from 9am to 5pm. For any queries or a quote, give us a call at 587-801-3091.
